channel.title: Subwoofer To The Max - Tropical Original
channel.description:
Hey folks, just recently now posted this track.
[Subwoofer to the max - Tropical Original](https://soundcloud.com/tropical_madman/subwoofer-to-the-max-topical)
I’ve been gone for a few weeks so I’m trying to make up the days I was gone. I’ve been making some really good piano lines. When I recently bought all the packs, i really wanted to get into more classic toned music.
But as always, take care, and happy making!
Tropical madman.
